Title: Mens Rotary Fusion chronograph rubber strap watch GS03623/C/19
Description: chapelle_jewellery Visit our eBay Shop Add us to your Favourites list > Subscribe to our Newsletter > About Chapelle Delivery The Chapelle Guarantee Mens Rotary Fusion chronograph rubber strap watch GS03623/C/19 RRP £250.00 Now £150.00 Description This all black, chunky mens Rotary Fusion watch has an imposing design. The smooth black rubber strap is fastened by a black buckle shaped to reflect the Rotary logo. The black ion plated stainless steel casing features a chunky black bezel that has six visible screw heads that give this watch a tough, industrial appeal. The round black dial has large white numbers and batons to clearly mark the hours and they stand out brilliantly against the black backing. Three small dials show the chronograph function in action and this function is controlled by the buttons located above and below the winder. The casing has a large design that measures 48mm wide including the winder and 10mm deep. This Rotary Fusion watch is waterproof and is sold with a lifetime Rotary warranty as long as you follow the Rotary service agreement. We are authorised stockists of Rotary watches and each one is sold in the official branded Rotary packaging.
